OL,3,CKanye's comments 'not reflective of
OL,4,CLondon' as rapper confirmed at Wireless
OL,6,FSadiq Khan said past comments by Kanye
OL,7,FWest were "offensive and wrong" as the
OL,8,FAmerican rapper was confirmed as the
OL,9,Fheadline act for three nights at this
OL,10,Fyear's Wireless Festival.
OL,12,FThe mayor said the performer's views
OL,13,Fwere "simply not reflective" of
OL,14,FLondon's values and the decision to
OL,15,Fbook him was taken by festival
OL,16,Forganisers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
