OL,3,CKanye's comments 'not reflective of
OL,4,CLondon' as rapper confirmed at Wireless
OL,6,FThe 48-year-old rapper, who now goes
OL,7,Fby the name Ye, has displayed erratic
OL,8,Fbehaviour and made controversial
OL,9,Fsocial media posts including some
OL,10,Fwhich were antisemitic.
OL,12,FIn 2018, West also gave a highly
OL,13,Fcontroversial interview to US outlet
OL,14,FTMZ about slavery.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
