OL,3,CKanye's comments 'not reflective of
OL,4,CLondon' as rapper confirmed at Wireless
OL,6,FHaringey Liberal Democrat Opposition
OL,7,FLeader, Cllr Luke Cawley-Harrison,
OL,8,Fsaid: "It is completely inappropriate
OL,9,Fand unacceptable for anyone with a
OL,10,Ftrack record of praising Adolf Hitler
OL,11,Fand declaring themselves a Nazi to be
OL,12,Fgiven a platform to perform -
OL,13,Fespecially in a publicly-owned park."
OL,15,FWest took out an advert in US
OL,16,Fnewspaper The Wall Street Journal to
OL,17,Fapologise for a number of statements
OL,18,Fabout Nazis, Adolf Hitler and Jews, in
OL,19,Fwhich he said he was not asking for
OL,20,F"sympathy or a free pass" and wanted
OL,21,Fto earn forgiveness from the public.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@YO]
