OL,3,CKanye's comments 'not reflective of
OL,4,CLondon' as rapper confirmed at Wireless
OL,6,FHe also apologised to the black
OL,7,Fcommunity, saying he had let them
OL,8,Fdown, and added that a car crash 25
OL,9,Fyears ago led to him being diagnosed
OL,10,Fas bipolar.
OL,12,FWireless Festival was contacted for
OL,13,Fcomment
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
